  "title": "Gold Nugget Recycling",
  "description": "Lets you smelt most gold-requiring items into Gold Nuggets. Must-have for Vanilla+ playthroughs.",
  "body": "---\n<p align=\"center\"?>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/gold-nugget-recycling\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bf84aa11b4afd69cdbd20a199bc6d93c50fac58b.png\" \n        alt=\"Modrinth\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        url=\"modrinth.com\"\n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/data-packs/gold-nugget-recycling\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3531508338997863e0b15c2252d16bf51ceb5669.png\" \n        alt=\"Curseforge\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/data-pack/gold-nugget-recycling\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eac8caa46edda35d821be9a2e1a8e16a00a9cadc.png\" \n        alt=\"Planet Minecraft\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n</p>  \n\n---\n**Gold Nugget Recycling** lets you smelt most gold-requiring items into Gold Nuggets. This can be useful when you craft too many Powered Rails or when you want some gold back from your Golden Carrots.\n\n**For Iron Nuggets check out [Iron Nugget Recycling](https://modrinth.com/datapack/iron-nugget-recycling)!**\n\n---\n\n<details>\n<summary>List of items that can now be smelted into Gold Nuggets</summary>\n \n- Glistering Melon\n- Golden Apple\n- Enchanted Golden Apple\n- Golden Carrot\n- Clock\n- Powered Rail\n- Light Weighted Pressure Plate\n- Gilded Blackstone\n\n</details>\n\n\n![Items that can now be smelted into Gold Nuggets](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EGpifGzW/images/188b44264ed0dc91eb738bca8e8fcdc477b4355f.png)\n\n\n---",
